videos.headline: Jacob Toppin sinks acrobatic spinning layup for Kentucky
videos.description: Jacob Toppin gets the quick pass inside and quickly spins in the air to avoid the defense and puts in a sweet layup for Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jacob Toppin sinks acrobatic spinning layup for Kentucky) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jacob Toppin gets up for big flush for Kentucky
videos.description: Sahvir Wheeler finds Jacob Toppin who cuts to the basket to throw down a powerful two-handed dunk for Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jacob Toppin gets up for big flush for Kentucky) 2021/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jamarion Sharp rolls his ankle vs. Kentucky
videos.description: Jamarion Sharp has to leave the game after he comes down and rolls his ankle on the foot of a defender.
